glosses: to stumble, trip, stagger, tottle, falter
to stumble, fumble the bag: to make a mistake or a blunder

etymology: By surface analysis, tökez- + -le, itself from Ottoman Turkish توكزیمك (tökezimek), further origin uncertain. According to Çağbayır, ultimately from the dialectal word tök (“back”). According to Nişanyan, related to dökmek (“to pour”).
